  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Specific CT Enteroclysis findings with or without other clinical and laboratory variables,
      can identify Crohn's disease patients who will response to medical therapy versus those who
      will either fail and require surgery or have uncontrolled disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
